snippet.title: Review Amber Court
snippet.description:
Amber Court. More information: https://hotelkdm.com/post/review-amber-court

Offering quality accommodations in the nightlife, casinos, family fun district of Genting Highlands, Genting Highlands Court Apartment is a popular pick for both business and leisure travelers. The city center is merely away and the airport can be reached within minutes. With its convenient location, the hotel offers easy access to the city's must-see destinations.

 Take advantage of a wealth of unrivaled services and amenities at this Genting Highlands hotel. A selection of top-class facilities such as car park, restaurant, laundry service, elevator, shops can be enjoyed at the hotel. 

 Genting Highlands Court Apartment is home to 2 bedrooms. All are tastefully furnished and many even provide such comforts as separate living room, non smoking rooms, balcony/terrace, television, kitchenette. Besides, the hotel's host of recreational offerings ensures you have plenty to do during your stay. Genting Highlands Court Apartment is an ideal place of stay for travelers seeking charm, comfort and convenience in Genting Highlands.
